channel.title: Help me please!
channel.description: How do i make it so it is PVP outside varrock bank (the one near G.E in retail) I am using project insanity base! Please help!

item.title: Help me please!
item.dc:creator: @Mendorphins Mendorphins
item.description:
@Mendorphins wrote:

Get the coords for the area that you want (imagine a square box surrounding the area and note down the bottom-left and the top-right corners) and then input them in to your isInWilderness (may not be called that) method in, I’m guessing, Player or PlayerHandler.java. Use what’s in this method as a guide on how to type it up, self explanatory really.
